Value ZONE_NAME (\S+)
Value DESCRIPTION (.*)
Value Required PRIORITY (\d+)
Value List INTERFACE ([A-Za-z]+[\d\/]+)
Value VRF (\S+)

Start
  ^# -> Continue.Record
  ^${ZONE_NAME}$$
  ^\s*vpn-instance\s+${VRF}\s+${ZONE_NAME}$$
  ^\s*description\s+${DESCRIPTION}$$
  ^\s*priority\s+is\s+${PRIORITY}$$
  ^\s*interface\s+of\s+the\s+zone\s+is\s+\((\d+)\):\s*$$
  ^\s+${INTERFACE}$$
  ^\s*$$